quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  42,30,"wma asabkm- 'ayuha alnas- min musibat fi dinikum wdnyakm fabima kasabtum min aldhunub walatham, wayaefu lakum rabukum ean kthyr min alsyyat, fala yuaakhidhukum bha"
  42,31,"wma antm- 'ayuha alnas- bimuejizin qudrat allah elykm, wala faytyh, wama lakum min dun allah min wly yatawalaa amwrkm, fywsl lakum almnafe, wala nasir yadfae eankum almdarra"
  42,32,"wmn ayatih aldalt ealaa qudratih albahrt wsltanh alqahir alsufun aleazimat kaljibal tajri fi albhr. 'iin yasha allah aladhi 'ajraa hadhih alsufun fi albahr yuskn alryh, ftabq alsufun swakn ealaa zahr albahr la tjry, 'iina fi jary hadhih alsufun wwqwfha fi albahr bqdrt allah laezat whjjana byint ealaa qudrat allah likuli sabaar ealaa taeat allh, shakur lnemh wafdalh"
  42,33,"wmn ayatih aldalt ealaa qudratih albahrt wsltanh alqahir alsufun aleazimat kaljibal tajri fi albhr. 'iin yasha allah aladhi 'ajraa hadhih alsufun fi albahr yuskn alryh, ftabq alsufun swakn ealaa zahr albahr la tjry, 'iina fi jary hadhih alsufun wwqwfha fi albahr bqdrt allah laezat whjjana byint ealaa qudrat allah likuli sabaar ealaa taeat allh, shakur lnemh wafdalh"
  42,34,"'aw yhlk alsufun bialgharaq bsbb dhanub ahlha, wyef ean kathir min aldhunub fala yeaqb elyha"
  42,35,"wyaelam aladhin yujadilun bialbatil fi ayatina aldalt ealaa twhydna, ma lahum min mhyd wala malja min eiqab allh, 'iidha eaqbhm ealaa dhunubihim wakufrihim bh"
  42,36,"fma awtytm- 'ayuha alnas- min shay' min almal 'aw albanin waghayr dhlk fahu matae lakum fi alhayat aldnya, surean ma yzwl, wama eind allah taealaa min naeim aljanat almuqim khayr wa'abqaa liladhin amanuu biallah wrslh, waealaa rabihim ytwklwn"
  42,37,"waldhyn yajtanibun kabayir ma nha allah enh, wama fahush wqabuh min 'anwae almeasy, wa'iidha ma ghadibuu ealaa man 'asa' 'iilayhim hum yaghfirun al'isa't, wysfhwn ean euqubat almsy'; tlbana lthwab allah taealaa wefwh, whdha min mhasn alakhlaq"
  42,38,"waldhyn astajabuu lirabihim hin deahm 'iilaa twhydh wtaeth, wa'aqamuu alsalat almafrudat bhdwdha fi awqatha, wa'iidha 'araduu amrana tshawru fyh, wamimaa aetynahm min al'amwal ytsdqwn fi sabil allh, wywdwn ma farad allah ealayhim min alhuquq lahlha min zakat wnfqt waghayr dhlk min wujuh al'infaq"
  42,39,"waldhyn 'iidha 'asabahum alzulm hum yantasirun mmn bgha ealayhim min ghyr 'ana yetdu, wa'iin sabaruu fafi eaqibat sbrhm khayr kthyr"
  42,40,"wjza' sayiyatan almusi' eqwbth bsyyt mithlaha min ghyr zyadt, faman eafa ean almsy', wtrk eqabh, wa'aslah alwdd baynah wabayn almefw eanh abtigha' wajh allh, f'ajr efwh dhlk ealaa allh. 'iina allah la yuhibu alzaalimin aladhin ybdwwn bialeudwan ealaa alnas, wysyywn 'ilyhm"
  42,41,wlmn antasar mmn zulmih min baed zulmih lah fawlyk ma ealayhim min mwakhdht
  42,42,"'inma almwakhdht ealaa aladhin yteddawn ealaa alnaas zlmana wedwanana, wytjawzwn alhdd aldhy abahh lahum rabuhum 'iilaa ma lam yadhan lahum fyh, fyfsdwn fi al'ard bighayr alhq, 'uwlayik lahum yawm alqiamat eadhab mulim mwje"
  42,43,"walaman sabar ealaa aladha, waqabil al'isa't balefw walsfh walssatr, 'iina dhlk min ezaym al'umur almshkwrt walafeal alhmydt alty 'amr allah bha, wrttab laha thwabana jryla wthna'an hmydana"